<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.3.2">
<l>pūcuñ cānteṉ ṉeñcamē puṉaiyuṅ kaṇṇi yeṉatuṭaiya</l>
<l>vāca kamcey mālaiyē vāṉpaṭ ṭāṭai yumaḵtē</l>
<l>tēca māṉa vaṇikalaṉu meṉkai kūppuc ceykaiyē</l>
<l>īcaṉ ñāla muṇṭumiḻnta ventai yēka mūrttikkē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The sandal that is smeared is my heart, and the garland</l>
<l>densely made from words is the celestial silk cloth,</l>
<l>and the action of folding my hands is the adorning ornament that is lustrous</l>
<l>of the unique form, our father who swallowed [and] spit out the world, the lord.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
